data.description: This home boasts a wealth of exquisite upgrades, including a top-of-the-line osmosis water filtration system. With a strong commitment to energy efficiency, it's designed to minimize utility expenses, ensuring that your costs stay low.  This meticulously cared-for home is captivating from the moment you arrive. This home is beyond compare, with just one year of occupancy, making it practically brand new. Every facet of this property exudes a fresh and pristine quality. Nestled in an ideal location, it's the perfect place to call home. The clean white kitchen effortlessly connects to the inviting living room, featuring a spacious island, ample cabinet space, and top-notch granite countertops that blend beautifully with the color scheme throughout. This kitchen is a perfect blend of beauty and practicality, creating an open and harmonious living space. The sizable backyard beckons with ample room for your dream pool, all while providing privacy of no rear neighbors. Make your appt. today
